reviews.text: Reasonable food at reasonable price in area with not that many choices.
Really nothing special!

HKD $42 for coffee and huge plate of rice with soup. Cantonese home cooked feel. This is a good refueling station if you are hungry. Meal combos come with omelete and garlic bread at $40 only. Besides here is broadway cinemathque with upmarket coffee place, go there for more international stuff.
Normal Hong Kong style restaurant, reasonable price and clean environment.
Good
